properties.Name: Refinery
properties.Description: An oil refinery or petroleum refinery is an industrial process plant where crude oil is processed and refined into more useful products such as petroleum naphtha, gasoline, diesel fuel, asphalt base, heating oil, kerosene, and liquefied petroleum gas.

Columns.Name: RefineryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Refinery.

Columns.Name: RefineryTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Refinery Type.

Columns.Name: RefineryLatitude
Columns.Description: The latitude location of the refinery.

Columns.Name: RefineryLongitude
Columns.Description: The longitude location of the refinery.

Columns.Name: RefineryFirstOperationalDate
Columns.Description: The first date of operation of the refinery.

Columns.Name: RefineryLastOperationalDate
Columns.Description: The last operation date of the refinery.

Columns.Name: RefineryFirstFeasibilityStudyStarted
Columns.Description: The date that the refinery feasibility study was started.

Columns.Name: RefineryFeasibilityStudyAcceptedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the refinery feasibility study was accepted.

Columns.Name: RefineryPermitsAppliedDate
Columns.Description: The date that permits were applied for.

Columns.Name: RefineryPermitsReceivedDate
Columns.Description: The date that permits were applied received for operation.

Columns.Name: RefineryConstructionStartDate
Columns.Description: The date that Refinery Construction started.

Columns.Name: RefineryConstructionCompletedDate
Columns.Description: The date that Refinery Construction was completed.

Columns.Name: RefineryFirstProductionDate
Columns.Description: The date of first production by the refinery.

Columns.Name: RefineryLastProductionDate
Columns.Description: The date of last production by the refinery.

Columns.Name: RefineryClosureDate
Columns.Description: The date that the refinery was closed.

Columns.Name: DailyCapacityBarrelsPerDay
Columns.Description: The daily capacity in barrels per day of the refinery.
